  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb \u0dc4\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd1\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d85\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db6\u0dbd\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dab\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The stolen cattle van collides with the high power pole",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Kalutara North Police said that they have received information that a luxury van suspected to have come to steal cattle illegally collided with a transformer with high-powered electric wires in Waskaduwa Gallupara this morning and two people were taken to hospital and the other people who came there have fled.",
        "The police say that two injured people have been admitted to the Panadura Base Hospital and investigations are being conducted to find the persons who fled.",
        "The front number plate of the van was missing, and the police found it inside the vehicle.",
        "All the rear seats of the van had been removed, and some ropes, which could be suspected to have been brought to tie the cows, could also be seen inside the vehicle.",
        "Local residents said that there was a smell of cows inside the vehicle and that there might have been cows at the time of the accident.",
        "Due to the accident, the electricity in the area was completely cut off, and the Galle highway was blocked by high voltage power lines, and the traffic on the Galle Road was disrupted."
      ],
